博伊塔諾在1994年的[[美國花式溜冰錦標賽|美國錦標賽]]中，在短節目後取得領先，但在自由滑後以6–3判分輸給{{tsl|en|Scott Davis (figure skater)|史考特·戴維斯}}。博伊塔諾列名美國奧運代表團，被認為是獎牌的有力爭奪者，但在短節目中空了[[一周半跳|三周半跳]]（這是他選手生涯第一次犯此失誤）<ref>{{Cite news   | last = Longman   | first = Jere   | title = WINTER OLYMPICS; Escapades on Ice: Favorites Go Slip-Sliding Away   | work =    | pages =    | language =    | publisher = [[New_York_Times|New York Times]]   | date = 1994-02-18   | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/18/sports/winter-olympics-escapades-on-ice-favorites-go-slip-sliding-away.html   | accessdate = 2014-04-26   | archive-date = 2014-04-26   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140426202231/http://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/18/sports/winter-olympics-escapades-on-ice-favorites-go-slip-sliding-away.html   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>。這個失誤使他掉到獎牌競爭圈之外，幸而自由滑表現不錯，最後列於第六名<ref>{{Cite news   | last = Vevsey   | first = Goerge   | title = Winter Olympics: Sports of the Times; Comforting to Know Standards Still Exist   | work =    | pages =    | language =    | publisher = [[New_York_Times|New York Times]]   | date = 1994-02-21   | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/21/sports/winter-olympics-sports-of-the-times-comforting-to-know-standards-still-exist.html   | accessdate = 2014-04-26   | archive-date = 2014-04-26   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140426202206/http://www.nytimes.com/1994/02/21/sports/winter-olympics-sports-of-the-times-comforting-to-know-standards-still-exist.html   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>。

之後，博伊塔諾重拾職業身分。1996年，他被選入{{tsl|en|World Figure Skating Hall of Fame|世界花式滑冰名人堂|世界花式滑冰名人堂}}與{{tsl|en|United States Figure Skating Hall of Fame|美國花式滑冰名人堂|美國花式滑冰名人堂}}。

==娛樂事業==
[[諷刺畫|諷刺畫]]形象的博伊塔諾，以「[[超級英雄|超級英雄]]」的樣貌，作為半常規角色出現在動畫《[[南方公園|南方公園]]》中，《[[南方公園劇場版|南方公園劇場版]]》（1999）甚至有一首名為「{{tsl|en|What Would Brian Boitano Do?|布萊恩·博伊塔諾要做啥？}}」的歌。歌名戲仿自流行標語「[[WWJD|耶穌要做啥？]]」。博伊塔諾也出現在作為《南方公園》原型的1995年耶誕節動畫《[[圣诞精神|耶誕精神]]》中，片中男孩們遇到他比碰到[[耶穌|耶穌]]或[[聖誕老人|聖誕老人]]還興奮。

2009年8月23日[[美食頻道_(美國)|美食頻道]]播出名為《{{tsl|en|What Would Brian Boitano Make?|布萊恩·博伊塔諾要煮啥？}}》的新節目，名稱與片頭曲顯然借自《[[南方公園劇場版|南方公園劇場版]]》。節目形式為博伊塔諾做菜給朋友吃，並在第一季結束後續訂全十集的第二季<ref>{{Cite web |title=What Would Brian Boitano Make Picked Up for Another Season |url=http://www.eatmedaily.com/2009/11/what-would-brian-boitano-make-picked-up-for-another-season/ |work=EatMeDaily.com |date=November 9, 2009 |accessdate=2014-05-18 |archive-date=2013-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131220094708/http://www.eatmedaily.com/2009/11/what-would-brian-boitano-make-picked-up-for-another-season/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==私生活==
博伊塔諾定居於[[舊金山|舊金山]]<ref name=residence/>。

2013年6月，俄羅斯公布了反同性戀法案，[[2014年冬季奥林匹克运动会#抵制|2014年索契冬奧因此遭到各界人士抵制]]<ref name=bloombergputinsigns>{{cite news|last=Rose|first=Scott|title=Putin signs law banning gay 'propaganda' among children|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-30/putin-signs-law-banning-gay-propaganda-among-children.html|newspaper=Bloomberg|date=1 July 2013|accessdate=2014-02-28|archive-date=2013-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131109074209/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-30/putin-signs-law-banning-gay-propaganda-among-children.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年12月，博伊塔諾被任命為[[2014年冬季奧林匹克運動會|2014冬奧]]美國代表團成員，與此同時他[[出櫃|出櫃]]<ref>[http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/sochi/2013/12/19/brian-boitano-announces-he-is-gay-sochi-delegation/4125427/ Brian Boitano announces he's gay before trip to Sochi] {{Wayback|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/olympics/sochi/2013/12/19/brian-boitano-announces-he-is-gay-sochi-delegation/4125427/ |date=20140223202116 }}, by Christine Brennan, at [[USA_Today|USA Today]]; published December 19, 2013; retrieved December 20, 2013</ref><ref name=Sieczkowski>{{cite web | url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/12/19/brian-boitano-comes-out-gay_n_4474418.html?utm_hp_ref=gay-voices | title=Figure Skater Brian Boitano Comes Out As Gay Ahead Of Sochi Olympics | publisher=''[[Huffington_Post|Huffington Post]]'' | date=December 19, 2013 | accessdate=December 19, 2013 | author=Sieczkowski, Cavan | archive-date=2013-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131223140631/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/12/19/brian-boitano-comes-out-gay_n_4474418.html?utm_hp_ref=gay-voices | dead-url=no }}</ref>。次年1月，博伊塔諾告訴[[美聯社|美聯社]]記者，在代表團名單公布之前，他並無意公開自己的性向<ref>{{cite news |first=Barry |last=Wilner |date=January 9, 2014 |url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/boitano-never-planned-gay-announcement |title=Boitano never planned gay announcement |work=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |accessdate=January 10, 2014 |archive-date=2014-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110223517/http://bigstory.ap.org/article/boitano-never-planned-gay-announcement |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

